45:18.500 --> 45:19.666
-You?
-Huh?

45:19.750 --> 45:22.166
Mm, uh, all right, yeah!

45:22.250 --> 45:23.250
She's very welcome.

45:23.333 --> 45:24.750
Yay!
[giggles]

45:24.833 --> 45:26.708
-[laughs]
-[manager] Okay, but be quiet.

45:26.791 --> 45:28.791
Right, I'll be quiet, Dad.

45:28.875 --> 45:31.083
[rain pattering]

45:32.166 --> 45:34.500
[Grace] Well, shall we get back to it?

45:34.583 --> 45:35.666
-[giggles]
-[Chuck slurps]

45:35.750 --> 45:38.125
Can you tell us about Larva
in greater detail?

45:38.208 --> 45:39.291
Uh-huh.

45:39.375 --> 45:41.625
Hmm. Well, uh...

45:41.708 --> 45:43.666
One minute, they're
at each other's throats,

45:43.750 --> 45:46.250
then, turn around, and they're
risking their lives for each other.

45:48.500 --> 45:50.166
[birds cawing]

45:50.250 --> 45:51.875
-[water splashes]
-[Chuck grunting]

45:51.958 --> 45:53.166
Fishy, you're mine!

45:53.250 --> 45:55.250
How long has it been since I've had fish?

45:55.333 --> 45:56.791
Whoa! Ooh, no!

45:56.875 --> 45:58.083
[groaning]

45:58.208 --> 45:59.916
-[thwacks]
-Oh!

46:01.875 --> 46:04.208
[groaning]

46:04.291 --> 46:06.166
-Huh? Huh?
-[Larva laughing]

46:06.250 --> 46:07.291
[both laughing]

46:07.375 --> 46:08.333
-[slaps]
-[thuds]

46:08.416 --> 46:09.875
[both laughing]

46:09.958 --> 46:12.333
[grunts]
I've had enough of you brats!

46:12.416 --> 46:13.833
Go away!

46:13.916 --> 46:15.333
[both blows raspberry]

46:15.416 --> 46:17.125
[grunting]
Take that!

46:17.208 --> 46:19.333
[Chuck] You guys ruin everything!

46:20.333 --> 46:21.250
-Oh!
-[thumps]

46:21.333 --> 46:22.875
[laughing]

46:24.208 --> 46:25.458
[splashes]

46:25.541 --> 46:27.583
-[screams]
-[squeals]

46:27.666 --> 46:30.041
[thudding]

46:32.958 --> 46:34.250
[screams]

46:37.208 --> 46:38.875
[yells]

46:39.458 --> 46:41.958
-[grunting]
-[Red squeals]

46:42.041 --> 46:43.083
[gasps]

46:44.625 --> 46:47.166
[mumbles, gasps]

46:47.541 --> 46:48.875
[muffled scream]

46:48.958 --> 46:50.625
-[squealing]
-[gasps]

46:51.916 --> 46:52.958
-[loud thump]
-[thuds]

46:54.375 --> 46:55.958
[both yelling]

46:56.208 --> 46:58.083
What is this?

46:58.166 --> 46:59.541
Hmm? What the...

46:59.625 --> 47:02.041
[Chuck] Get off my sacred food!

47:02.125 --> 47:03.291
-[thuds]
-[groans]

47:04.958 --> 47:06.708
Oh, you beauty!

47:06.791 --> 47:08.458
[smooches, laughs]

47:09.250 --> 47:10.375
[gasps]

47:10.458 --> 47:12.791
[Chuck humming]

47:13.250 --> 47:15.250
You're gonna taste amazing!

47:15.333 --> 47:16.791
Now, make a little fire.

47:16.875 --> 47:18.208
-[squeaks]
-[humming]

47:18.291 --> 47:19.666
[groaning]

47:20.208 --> 47:21.666
-[Chuck] Yes! Burn, baby!
-[hisses]

47:21.750 --> 47:23.416
Burn! Burn! Yes!

47:24.250 --> 47:26.291
-[thuds]
-No! So close!

47:26.375 --> 47:27.791
And yet so far!

47:27.875 --> 47:29.041
But hey!

47:29.125 --> 47:30.750
-What's this?
-[match rasps]

47:30.833 --> 47:32.041
[snickers]

47:32.125 --> 47:33.291
-Lucky me!
-[flame crackles]

47:33.375 --> 47:34.958
Here we go! Here we go!

47:35.083 --> 47:37.791
[grunting, yelling]

47:37.875 --> 47:40.208
[pants]

47:40.291 --> 47:41.833
-[sizzles]
-Huh?

47:41.916 --> 47:44.041
[screams]

47:44.125 --> 47:46.041
[muffled screaming]

47:46.666 --> 47:48.791
[gasps, screams]

47:48.875 --> 47:50.625
Mm. Lovely aroma.

47:50.708 --> 47:52.291
-[Yellow grunting]
-Hmm? What?

47:52.875 --> 47:54.125
Why you...

47:54.208 --> 47:55.333
[puffs]

47:56.166 --> 47:57.291
[match rasps]

47:57.375 --> 47:59.416
[snickers, gasps]

47:59.500 --> 48:01.125
[groans]
Go away!

48:01.208 --> 48:02.333
-[match rasps]
-[Yellow puffs]

48:02.416 --> 48:03.708
[gasps]

48:03.791 --> 48:05.125
Stop it, all right?

48:05.208 --> 48:06.416
I mean it!

48:06.916 --> 48:09.500
Just let me grill my yummy fishy.

48:10.416 --> 48:11.333
Huh?

48:11.416 --> 48:13.208
[yells]

48:13.666 --> 48:14.708
Huh?

48:14.791 --> 48:16.000
-[sizzles]
-Ah!

48:16.375 --> 48:17.875
-That's how you want it?
-[match snaps]

48:17.958 --> 48:18.791
[gasps]

48:18.875 --> 48:20.333
-[sizzles]
-Hot!

48:20.416 --> 48:21.708
[grunts]

48:21.791 --> 48:23.083
[screams]

48:23.416 --> 48:24.666
Now, it's your turn!

48:24.750 --> 48:26.083
Burn!

48:26.166 --> 48:27.333
[sizzles]

48:27.416 --> 48:28.708
[screams]

48:30.250 --> 48:31.250
[grunts]

48:31.333 --> 48:32.500
[yelps]

48:33.875 --> 48:35.333
-[bones crack]
-[whimpering]

48:35.416 --> 48:36.916
[groans]

48:37.666 --> 48:39.416
-All right, fish, where were we?
-[thuds]

48:39.500 --> 48:41.041
-[puffs]
-[screams]

48:41.666 --> 48:43.333
-Seriously?
-[screams]

48:45.166 --> 48:49.125
-[whistles]
-[yelps]

48:49.208 --> 48:50.541
Dinner is finally served.

48:50.625 --> 48:51.791
-[splashes]
-[Chuck groaning]

48:51.875 --> 48:54.208
[whale hums]

48:54.916 --> 48:56.958
[whimpers, screams]

48:57.958 --> 48:59.875
Why are you doing this? Why? Why?

48:59.958 --> 49:01.708
Well, we'll see who wins.
[gasps]

49:01.791 --> 49:03.333
[Chuck] Only one match left.

49:03.416 --> 49:05.583
[gasps, grunts]

49:06.125 --> 49:07.791
[Chuck] Stubborn little booger.

49:07.875 --> 49:08.791
All right.

49:09.625 --> 49:10.750
Draw.

49:10.833 --> 49:13.458
[tense music]

49:13.541 --> 49:15.083
-Ooh, look! What's that?
-Huh?

49:15.166 --> 49:17.458
[laughs]

49:17.541 --> 49:18.458
[gasps, screams]

49:19.708 --> 49:21.000
-[farts]
-[snickers]

49:21.083 --> 49:21.916
-[thwacks]
-Huh?

49:24.791 --> 49:27.875
[grunting]

49:29.791 --> 49:30.833
[laughs]

49:31.541 --> 49:32.625
[farts]

49:32.708 --> 49:33.958
[screams]

49:34.375 --> 49:36.083
Oh, that's so disgusting!

49:36.166 --> 49:37.875
Huh? Where's my match?

49:38.958 --> 49:40.000
[gasps]

49:40.416 --> 49:42.083
Oh, please don't let it go out!

49:42.166 --> 49:44.250
Curse that farting bug!
[gasps]

49:45.958 --> 49:47.208
[Chuck] Come on!

49:47.291 --> 49:49.416
[yells]

49:49.500 --> 49:51.791
[farting]

49:51.875 --> 49:54.416
Hold on, flame, here I come!

49:54.500 --> 49:57.291
Gas boom!

49:57.375 --> 49:59.125
[flame roars]

50:00.833 --> 50:02.333
[flame crackles]

50:02.416 --> 50:03.875
-[panting]
-[sighs]

50:03.958 --> 50:04.916
It worked!

50:05.666 --> 50:08.958
It's burning! I win! I win!
[laughs]

50:09.041 --> 50:10.333
[gasps]

50:10.416 --> 50:11.833
[laughing]

50:12.208 --> 50:14.375
Beautiful fire!
[laughs]

50:14.458 --> 50:15.708
[squeals]

50:15.791 --> 50:17.000
[screams]

50:17.750 --> 50:20.458
[grunting]

50:21.958 --> 50:24.333
-[grunts]
-[thumps]

50:24.416 --> 50:26.458
-[gasps for air]
-[muffled yelling]

50:27.875 --> 50:30.250
[laughs, screams]

50:31.916 --> 50:33.083
[thwacks]

50:33.166 --> 50:36.625
-[thumping]
-[groaning]

50:38.083 --> 50:39.875
[heart beating]

50:39.958 --> 50:42.416
[ominous music]

50:44.333 --> 50:45.375
[popping]

50:45.458 --> 50:46.958
Happy fish party!

50:47.041 --> 50:48.375
-[thwacks]
-[groaning]

50:49.250 --> 50:50.833
-[splashes]
-[Chuck] No.

50:50.916 --> 50:52.583
Come back! Come back!

50:52.666 --> 50:53.875
[sobs]

50:57.208 --> 50:58.333
[burbles]

50:58.875 --> 51:01.041
[narrator] <i>The life of a pollack fish.</i>

51:01.500 --> 51:05.291
<i>After the narrow escape,
the pollack's relief is short-lived</i>

51:05.875 --> 51:09.166
<i>for there are countless dangers
that lurk in the ocean.</i>

51:09.750 --> 51:13.250
<i>However, in the fierce struggle
for survival with its natural enemies,</i>

51:13.333 --> 51:16.291
<i>the pollack has become
stronger and smarter.</i>

51:16.833 --> 51:19.250
<i>Our pollack turns out to be a female.</i>

51:20.208 --> 51:24.958
<i>With spawning season upon her,
many males begin their overtures.</i>

51:25.500 --> 51:28.500
<i>The flashy movements of one male
are eye-catching.</i>

51:28.583 --> 51:30.625
<i>The female pollack is interested.</i>

51:33.625 --> 51:36.541
-<i>So begins their pollack romance.</i>
-[smooching]

51:36.625 --> 51:37.583
[screams]

51:37.666 --> 51:39.000
[narrator] <i>First comes love.</i>

51:39.458 --> 51:41.250
<i>And then, of course, comes...</i>

51:42.166 --> 51:45.541
<i>a hundred thousand to a million
little fishy miracles.</i>

51:46.291 --> 51:50.625
<i>And when the time comes,
they will leave their parents' embrace</i>

51:50.708 --> 51:53.333
<i>to start a new journey in the vast world.</i>

51:54.166 --> 52:00.166
<i>Like their parents, they must survive
many hardships and seek out a partner,</i>

52:00.250 --> 52:04.458
<i>so that they may fill the world
with little miracles of their very own.</i>

52:05.416 --> 52:07.125
<i>The life of a pollack fish.</i>

52:07.208 --> 52:09.666
<i>Fin. The end.</i>

52:09.750 --> 52:11.250
-Wow! Awesome!
-[chef] For real?

52:11.333 --> 52:13.375
Those bugs are like a phoenix
or something.

52:13.458 --> 52:17.458
Yes, they are. Those little boogers
could survive any danger ever! Uh...

52:17.541 --> 52:19.083
-[chuckles]
-[gasps]

52:19.166 --> 52:20.250
[groans]

52:20.333 --> 52:21.541
-Uh...
-Chuck.

52:21.625 --> 52:24.291
Lots of people seem interested
in this story of yours.

52:24.375 --> 52:26.500
It's the first time that's happened.

52:26.791 --> 52:27.958
-[Wendy] Mister!
-Huh?

52:28.041 --> 52:30.583
Please! Please keep telling us your story!

52:31.208 --> 52:34.958
This is the best story I've heard
in my 84 years on Earth.

52:35.083 --> 52:36.250
So true!

52:36.333 --> 52:38.583
I'm dying to try some of that
tasty bug cuisine.

52:38.666 --> 52:40.125
Mmm-mmm.

52:40.208 --> 52:43.333
Your lunch is on me,
if you agree to tell us some more.

52:43.416 --> 52:44.833
-Uh...
-[Grace] Chuck?

52:46.041 --> 52:48.375
-Chuck!
-[gasps]

52:48.458 --> 52:51.000
Are you all right with them hearing
the rest of the interview?

52:51.750 --> 52:54.291
Uh... Mm-hm. You bet.

52:55.208 --> 52:58.125
I'm really touched you all wanna hear
what I went through.

52:58.208 --> 53:00.125
-[Grace] Uh...
-Yay!

53:00.208 --> 53:03.458
Uh, um... Great! Good!

53:04.083 --> 53:05.166
Hmm.

53:05.250 --> 53:08.125
If I'm honest here,
this is hard to swallow.

53:08.208 --> 53:10.291
It sounds like a fantasy movie.

53:11.625 --> 53:13.458
And you haven't heard the half of it.

53:14.375 --> 53:17.708
I haven't even gotten to the crazy stuff.

53:18.125 --> 53:20.166
[ominous music]

53:20.250 --> 53:22.500
-[Chuck humming]
-[thumping]

53:24.041 --> 53:26.291
Huh? Why is it so cloudy today?

53:26.583 --> 53:29.708
Ah, who cares?
I've still got the best boat.

53:29.791 --> 53:31.375
[laughs]

53:31.458 --> 53:32.791
And today, wait for it!

53:32.875 --> 53:34.708
We add the umbrella sail!

53:34.791 --> 53:36.958
-[laughs]
-[bottle plops]

53:37.041 --> 53:38.916
[humming]

53:39.458 --> 53:40.500
-[wood thuds]
-[gasps]

53:40.583 --> 53:42.708
Uh, wha... Why is this...

53:42.791 --> 53:44.125
-Huh?
-[squeaking]

53:46.500 --> 53:48.791
-[gasps]
-[snickers]

53:49.625 --> 53:50.625
[thumps]

53:51.958 --> 53:54.250
Did I ever tell you until college,

53:54.333 --> 53:56.291
I was on the soccer team!

53:56.708 --> 53:59.208
Ha! Rotten bugs!

53:59.291 --> 54:01.625
-[wind whooshing]
-Ha, breeze feels nice.

54:02.250 --> 54:03.500
-[umbrella pops]
-[gasps]

54:03.583 --> 54:05.416
Oh, no! Ah!

54:05.500 --> 54:07.041
-[water splashes]
-[gasps]

54:07.125 --> 54:08.416
[Chuck sobs]

54:08.500 --> 54:10.583
[yells]

54:10.666 --> 54:12.125
[laughing]

54:12.208 --> 54:13.125
[thwacks]

54:13.208 --> 54:14.958
It's all because of you, bugs!

54:16.625 --> 54:18.916
-[thunder rumbles]
-[Chuck] It's all because of you, bugs!

54:20.291 --> 54:22.083
[both panting]

54:22.166 --> 54:24.541
Ah, this ends right now, you hear?

54:24.625 --> 54:25.791
No, you don't!

54:25.875 --> 54:27.458
-[thuds]
-[groans, gasps]

54:27.958 --> 54:29.875
You're done living up to your name.

54:29.958 --> 54:31.416
[screams]

54:31.500 --> 54:33.291
[squeals]

54:34.708 --> 54:36.166
[screams, groans]

54:36.250 --> 54:37.833
[thunder rumbles]

54:37.916 --> 54:40.041
-[crackling]
-[groaning]

54:43.833 --> 54:46.375
-[thudding]
-[groaning]

54:46.458 --> 54:47.916
[splashes]

54:53.500 --> 54:55.541
-[birds cawing]
-[waves crashing]

54:55.625 --> 54:57.958
[Chuck] Uh... Oh, my head.

54:58.041 --> 54:59.583
What happened again?

54:59.666 --> 55:01.541
Oh, right, lightning.

55:01.625 --> 55:03.375
Those annoying bugs.

55:03.458 --> 55:04.958
[groans]
Little monsters.

55:05.083 --> 55:08.125
I can't wait to turn them
into puddles of goo on the beach.

55:09.333 --> 55:10.958
[gasps]

55:12.166 --> 55:14.416
[gasping]

55:14.708 --> 55:16.166
[screams]

55:17.041 --> 55:17.916
What the...

55:18.000 --> 55:19.791
Who's that? This is not happening!

55:19.875 --> 55:21.791
This can't be!
[whimpers]

55:21.875 --> 55:22.750
Huh?

55:23.041 --> 55:24.250
[gasps]

55:26.541 --> 55:28.541
[slurps, munches]

55:28.625 --> 55:29.791
[screams]

55:31.500 --> 55:33.291
-[Chuck] A bug! A bug is me!
-[farts]

55:34.000 --> 55:35.166
[both scream]

55:35.250 --> 55:37.458
What have you done to me,
you horrible nightmare?

55:37.541 --> 55:40.833
-[thwacking]
-[both grunting]

55:41.416 --> 55:43.208
-[bird screeches]
-[both] Hmm?

55:43.291 --> 55:44.958
[wings flapping]

55:45.041 --> 55:46.375
-Food!
-[Yellow mumbles]

55:48.916 --> 55:50.625
Oh! Finally!
[pants]

55:50.708 --> 55:52.166
Uh? So big!

55:53.375 --> 55:54.750
-[caws]
-[screams]

55:55.375 --> 55:56.791
-[thuds]
-[screams]

55:58.208 --> 55:59.666
[laughs]

55:59.750 --> 56:01.625
[Chuck panting]

56:03.416 --> 56:04.958
[cawing]

56:05.041 --> 56:07.958
-[thumping]
-[gasping]

56:08.958 --> 56:10.125
[groans]

56:10.791 --> 56:11.791
Stay back!

56:11.875 --> 56:13.000
Nice chicken.

56:13.083 --> 56:14.500
[Chuck whimpering]

56:15.208 --> 56:16.833
[screams]

56:16.916 --> 56:18.416
[mumbles]

56:18.500 --> 56:20.291
-[smooches]
-[gasps]

56:20.375 --> 56:21.958
-[nervous chuckle]
-[groans]

56:22.083 --> 56:24.541
-[yells]
-[thwacking]

56:26.083 --> 56:27.250
-[thumps]
-[groans]

56:28.250 --> 56:29.916
-[Chuck] Huh? You now?
-[metal clanks]

56:30.000 --> 56:31.500
[Chuck] Come on!

56:31.583 --> 56:33.666
Sorry, I pushed you so darn hard.

56:33.750 --> 56:35.875
-[robotic muttering]
-[Chuck] Please don't hurt me!

56:38.291 --> 56:39.875
-[Chuck yells]
-[robotic muttering]

56:41.541 --> 56:44.166
[groaning]

56:48.541 --> 56:49.791
Ooh!

56:49.875 --> 56:51.958
[groaning]

56:52.041 --> 56:54.291
[laughs]

56:54.375 --> 56:56.541
[thumps]

56:57.583 --> 56:59.833
[cheers, gasps]

57:00.333 --> 57:01.791
[gasps, yelps]

57:01.875 --> 57:03.041
Huh?

57:03.125 --> 57:04.375
-[cheers]
-[stomach rumbles]

57:05.500 --> 57:06.958
Oh!

57:07.958 --> 57:09.458
[grunting]

57:10.500 --> 57:11.958
[farts]

57:12.208 --> 57:13.541
[grunting]

57:14.125 --> 57:17.250
[farting]

57:18.625 --> 57:20.750
[birds chirping]

57:21.458 --> 57:22.583
[groans]

57:23.541 --> 57:25.750
-[screams]
-[mumbles]

57:25.833 --> 57:27.666
Ah! Somebody help!

57:29.791 --> 57:30.833
-[thuds]
-[gasps]

57:31.250 --> 57:33.333
I'm trapped in a madhouse!

57:33.416 --> 57:34.875
[munching]

57:36.333 --> 57:37.541
Mm! Yum!

57:40.333 --> 57:43.375
[sobbing]

57:43.458 --> 57:46.250
I'm a gross and revolting ugly bug.

57:46.333 --> 57:48.000
Chicken tried to eat me whole.

57:48.083 --> 57:49.458
That even worse...

57:49.541 --> 57:50.833
[munching]

57:51.500 --> 57:53.375
[Red laughs]

57:54.583 --> 57:56.291
[gasps]

57:56.416 --> 57:58.666
[chomps, giggles]

57:59.708 --> 58:02.541
I just thought of them
as dumb little awful bugs.

58:02.625 --> 58:05.125
-[ship horn blares]
-Huh? What? Sounds like... Oh, my!

58:06.416 --> 58:08.500
[pants, gasps]

58:08.583 --> 58:10.208
[ship horn blares]

58:10.291 --> 58:11.333
[gasps]

58:11.416 --> 58:13.500
Ah! I'm here! Please help!

58:13.583 --> 58:15.500
Huh? What the...

58:15.583 --> 58:17.041
Oh, bug, right.

58:17.125 --> 58:18.083
-[thunder rumbles]
-Huh?

58:18.166 --> 58:20.250
[Chuck] Just like the last storm.

58:22.041 --> 58:23.000
Huh?

58:23.083 --> 58:24.500
[Chuck] Really?

58:25.041 --> 58:26.291
All right!

58:27.416 --> 58:29.583
[Chuck] Look. Yum, yum, yum!
You know you want it!

58:29.666 --> 58:30.958
[Yellow mumbling]

58:32.875 --> 58:35.416
-[Chuck groans]
-[slurping]

58:36.125 --> 58:37.333
No, not yet!

58:37.416 --> 58:39.333
[gasps]
Huh? All right!

58:39.416 --> 58:41.166
[Chuck] Here it comes!

58:41.250 --> 58:43.166
-[bird screeches]
-[Chuck screams]

58:43.250 --> 58:45.416
Not now! Let go of me!

58:45.500 --> 58:46.791
[Chuck grunts]

58:46.875 --> 58:49.541
Please! That boat was my ticket back home!

58:49.625 --> 58:50.958
[sobbing]

58:51.541 --> 58:53.541
-Huh?
-[farting]

58:53.625 --> 58:56.875
[all screaming]

58:56.958 --> 58:58.416
-[bird caws]
-[groans]

58:58.500 --> 58:59.500
[gasps]

58:59.583 --> 59:01.083
-[farts]
-[yelps]

59:01.166 --> 59:02.875
[crackling]

59:04.541 --> 59:05.375
[screams]

59:06.000 --> 59:08.666
[gasps, panting]

59:08.750 --> 59:10.625
[mumbling]

59:12.833 --> 59:13.958
[sighs]

59:14.083 --> 59:15.833
Of course, it was only a dream.

59:15.916 --> 59:18.958
-[loud blaring]
-Huh? Is that a ship?

59:19.041 --> 59:20.500
Yo, over here!

59:20.583 --> 59:22.125
There's someone here!

59:22.208 --> 59:25.041
-[Yellow farting]
-Uh...

59:25.125 --> 59:26.208
[both laughing]

59:27.125 --> 59:28.875
Why, you little rotten bugs!

59:28.958 --> 59:30.750
Think that's funny, do you?

59:30.833 --> 59:32.166
[both whimpering]

59:32.291 --> 59:33.583
[groans]

59:33.666 --> 59:34.666
[sighs]

59:35.791 --> 59:36.708
Hmm.

59:37.916 --> 59:39.708
[Chuck] I'm sorry for acting so mean.

59:40.083 --> 59:41.541
[yells, grunts]

59:41.625 --> 59:43.041
Ow! That hurts!

59:43.125 --> 59:45.708
Why, you rotten little bugs!
[groans]

59:45.791 --> 59:48.750
After that stuff, I was able
to understand them better.

59:50.208 --> 59:51.750
-[Grace] Oh.
-[slurps]

59:52.458 --> 59:54.250
[insect buzzing]

59:54.541 --> 59:55.375
Huh?

59:55.458 --> 59:56.541
-[loud thump]
-[all gasps]

59:56.625 --> 59:59.041
Uh! It was a force of habit.

1:00:00.250 --> 1:00:02.583
-I'm sorry!
-All right. There, there.

1:00:02.666 --> 1:00:04.166
[chef sobbing]

1:00:04.250 --> 1:00:05.416
[clears throat]

1:00:05.500 --> 1:00:09.375
So you're telling us you shared a bond
with your bug buddies?

1:00:09.458 --> 1:00:10.583
Yeah.

1:00:10.666 --> 1:00:12.291
But not just my bug buddies.

1:00:12.375 --> 1:00:14.958
With Clara, Booby, Crabsformer.

1:00:15.083 --> 1:00:16.416
Mudskippers as well.

1:00:16.708 --> 1:00:19.208
We were trying
to survive together, after all.

1:00:19.291 --> 1:00:20.541
[all] Hmm.

1:00:20.625 --> 1:00:22.791
Oh! I'm sorry, little fly!

1:00:22.875 --> 1:00:25.541
-[rain pattering]
-[thunder rumbles]

1:00:25.625 --> 1:00:27.375
Ah, the thunder's so loud!

1:00:27.458 --> 1:00:29.000
-[chef] Oh!
-Wendy, it's all right.

1:00:29.083 --> 1:00:30.541
Daddy's here, darling.

1:00:30.625 --> 1:00:32.083
Is it gonna storm?

1:00:32.166 --> 1:00:34.666
Looks like we're in
for some temperamental weather.

1:00:35.166 --> 1:00:36.166
Weather.

1:00:36.250 --> 1:00:38.875
The weather on the island
was absolutely cuckoo.

1:00:38.958 --> 1:00:41.333
Either burning hot or freezing cold.

1:00:41.416 --> 1:00:43.666
[Chuck] Freak tornadoes
would rip up out of nowhere.

1:00:43.750 --> 1:00:45.333
[wind howling]

1:00:45.416 --> 1:00:46.291
[thuds]

1:00:46.375 --> 1:00:49.625
[Chuck] Why have icebergs
completely surrounded the island?

1:00:49.708 --> 1:00:52.000
[Chuck screams]

1:00:52.083 --> 1:00:53.958
[air hisses]

1:00:54.333 --> 1:00:56.000
-Huh?
-[Clara whines]

1:00:56.083 --> 1:00:57.458
[all gasp]

1:00:57.541 --> 1:00:58.708
[wind whooshes]

1:01:05.083 --> 1:01:06.416
-[robotic mutter]
-[crab burbles]

1:01:08.875 --> 1:01:10.583
[squawks]

1:01:11.666 --> 1:01:13.250
-[squeals]
-Huh?

1:01:14.250 --> 1:01:16.000
[Chuck] Save me!

1:01:16.083 --> 1:01:18.958
-[flame crackles]
-I'm not gonna be an icicle.

1:01:19.875 --> 1:01:21.958
We have to burn everything we can.

1:01:22.625 --> 1:01:25.666
[thudding]

1:01:29.166 --> 1:01:30.458
[cracks]

1:01:30.541 --> 1:01:31.708
[rips]

1:01:31.791 --> 1:01:33.166
[yells]

1:01:33.791 --> 1:01:36.083
No! The fire's going out!

1:01:36.166 --> 1:01:37.333
There's nothing else to burn.

1:01:37.416 --> 1:01:38.708
[Chuck] What do we do?

1:01:38.791 --> 1:01:40.083
[gasps]

1:01:41.833 --> 1:01:42.791
[pops]

1:01:43.416 --> 1:01:44.500
[mumbles]

1:01:45.375 --> 1:01:46.833
[grunts]

1:01:46.916 --> 1:01:50.500
[muttering]

1:01:51.041 --> 1:01:52.750
[munches]

1:01:52.833 --> 1:01:53.791
[squeals]

1:01:55.375 --> 1:01:56.416
[burps]

1:01:56.791 --> 1:01:58.583
[gasps, screams]

1:01:58.666 --> 1:02:00.458
[all gasping]

1:02:00.541 --> 1:02:03.666
-[air hissing]
-[gasping]

1:02:05.250 --> 1:02:06.916
[Chuck] Lighter. My lighter!

1:02:07.000 --> 1:02:08.291
-There you are.
-[lighter clicks]

1:02:09.958 --> 1:02:11.541
[all gasp]

1:02:11.625 --> 1:02:14.500
[ominous music]

1:02:20.666 --> 1:02:22.833
[rattling]

1:02:22.916 --> 1:02:25.625
[farting]

1:02:27.166 --> 1:02:28.958
[clinking]

1:02:34.375 --> 1:02:35.833
[farting]

1:02:35.916 --> 1:02:37.333
[roars]

1:02:38.583 --> 1:02:40.916
[whooshing]

1:02:43.000 --> 1:02:44.875
[clanking]

1:02:44.958 --> 1:02:48.291
[flame roars]

1:02:48.375 --> 1:02:50.583
[sizzles]

1:02:51.625 --> 1:02:52.916
Ha-ha!

1:02:54.208 --> 1:02:55.291
Huh?

1:02:55.375 --> 1:02:56.541
[both whimper]

1:02:57.416 --> 1:02:58.250
[laughing]

1:02:58.708 --> 1:03:00.125
We're saved, Clara!

1:03:00.208 --> 1:03:01.166
We're saved!

1:03:01.250 --> 1:03:03.000
-We thawed up! Yahoo!
-[barks]

1:03:03.083 --> 1:03:04.166
[laughs]

1:03:04.250 --> 1:03:06.625
[groans]
What is that stink?

1:03:08.708 --> 1:03:12.458
[groaning, farting]

1:03:16.166 --> 1:03:17.625
[mutters]

1:03:17.708 --> 1:03:18.750
[smacks lips]

1:03:19.416 --> 1:03:20.458
[gasps]

1:03:22.958 --> 1:03:25.916
[thunder rumbles]

1:03:26.000 --> 1:03:27.750
[both laughing]

1:03:27.833 --> 1:03:29.041
[thuds]

1:03:29.125 --> 1:03:31.833
[mumbles]

1:03:32.625 --> 1:03:33.958
[both gasp]

1:03:34.041 --> 1:03:35.791
[both scream]

1:03:35.875 --> 1:03:38.375
-[thwacks]
-[all shout]

1:03:38.458 --> 1:03:39.750
[thumps]

1:03:40.083 --> 1:03:42.375
[both mumbling]

1:03:42.458 --> 1:03:44.416
[thunder rumbles]

1:03:46.166 --> 1:03:47.750
[screeching]

1:03:47.833 --> 1:03:49.375
[both scream]

1:03:49.458 --> 1:03:51.208
[thudding]

1:03:51.708 --> 1:03:54.250
[all gasp, scream]

1:03:55.166 --> 1:03:57.083
[groans]
Hungry.

1:03:57.166 --> 1:03:58.625
[bugs panting]

1:03:58.708 --> 1:04:00.041
You little devils!

1:04:00.125 --> 1:04:01.750
-[thumps]
-What the...

1:04:02.166 --> 1:04:04.125
Uh? Wha... A fish?

1:04:04.208 --> 1:04:07.458
Ooh! I love you!

1:04:07.541 --> 1:04:10.666
[smooches]

1:04:10.750 --> 1:04:12.166
-[thumps]
-Huh?

1:04:12.250 --> 1:04:13.583
[clanks]

1:04:14.041 --> 1:04:15.500
What's happening?

1:04:16.083 --> 1:04:17.708
-[barking]
-Cla... Clara?

1:04:17.791 --> 1:04:18.958
[grunts]

1:04:19.041 --> 1:04:20.875
Clara, why are you flying?

1:04:20.958 --> 1:04:22.208
[groaning]

1:04:22.291 --> 1:04:24.041
[wind howling]

1:04:24.125 --> 1:04:25.291
What the...

1:04:25.375 --> 1:04:26.500
Typhoon!

1:04:26.583 --> 1:04:28.041
[screams]

1:04:29.625 --> 1:04:31.333
[all screaming]

1:04:31.416 --> 1:04:32.958
[groans, gasps]

1:04:33.041 --> 1:04:34.583
[bird squawks]

1:04:34.666 --> 1:04:35.708
[thumps]

1:04:37.000 --> 1:04:38.500
[all groaning]

1:04:40.541 --> 1:04:42.375
Save me, please!

1:04:42.458 --> 1:04:45.000
-[thudding]
-[Chuck whimpering]

1:04:46.083 --> 1:04:47.541
[squawks]

1:04:47.625 --> 1:04:49.291
[thuds]

1:04:49.375 --> 1:04:51.250
[panting]

1:04:52.916 --> 1:04:54.375
[shrieks]

1:04:54.458 --> 1:04:56.041
Ah, cave door's blocked!

1:04:56.416 --> 1:04:58.125
[grunts]
Huh?

1:04:58.208 --> 1:04:59.166
[mumbles]

1:04:59.250 --> 1:05:00.458
-Ooh!
-[all mumble]

1:05:00.541 --> 1:05:02.083
[Clara barking]

1:05:02.166 --> 1:05:03.375
[Chuck gasping]

1:05:04.500 --> 1:05:07.291
[screams]

1:05:07.833 --> 1:05:10.083
Oh, quick! Quick!

1:05:10.166 --> 1:05:12.291
[grunts]
Come on!

1:05:12.375 --> 1:05:13.750
[Chuck] Please.

1:05:19.958 --> 1:05:21.708
-[thwacks]
-Ooh!

1:05:21.791 --> 1:05:22.875
[thwacking]

1:05:22.958 --> 1:05:24.291
[groaning]

1:05:24.958 --> 1:05:26.791
-[thwack]
-[Chuck] Ah!

1:05:26.875 --> 1:05:28.791
Ugh, my butt!

1:05:28.875 --> 1:05:30.958
-[all gasp]
-The rock is coming loose.

1:05:32.416 --> 1:05:33.791
[grunting]

1:05:33.875 --> 1:05:34.916
[wind whooshing]

1:05:35.583 --> 1:05:37.458
Can't keep holding on!

1:05:37.541 --> 1:05:38.500
[gasps]

1:05:38.583 --> 1:05:40.125
[all grunting]

1:05:40.208 --> 1:05:41.458
You guys...

1:05:41.958 --> 1:05:43.583
[gasps]
Huh?

1:05:43.666 --> 1:05:44.791
[all gasp]

1:05:44.875 --> 1:05:46.291
Uh, has it passed?

1:05:46.375 --> 1:05:47.958
[all cheering]

1:05:49.416 --> 1:05:50.333
Whew!

1:05:50.416 --> 1:05:51.541
Uh. Huh?

1:05:51.625 --> 1:05:52.708
[whimpering]

1:05:52.791 --> 1:05:54.541
I guess it hasn't passed!

1:05:54.625 --> 1:05:55.875
[groans]

1:05:55.958 --> 1:05:58.291
[screams]

1:05:59.083 --> 1:06:00.875
[squawks]

1:06:00.958 --> 1:06:02.333
Clara!

1:06:02.416 --> 1:06:03.750
[all screaming]

1:06:04.916 --> 1:06:07.083
[grunting]

1:06:11.625 --> 1:06:13.041
[clatters]

1:06:13.125 --> 1:06:14.958
[grunts]
Huh?

1:06:15.041 --> 1:06:16.083
[whooshes]

1:06:16.166 --> 1:06:17.208
[screaming]

1:06:17.291 --> 1:06:19.166
-[grunts, screams]
-[thuds]

1:06:20.083 --> 1:06:21.125
[gasps]

1:06:21.708 --> 1:06:24.416
-[clinking]
-[grunting]

1:06:24.500 --> 1:06:25.750
[snickers]
Huh?

1:06:25.833 --> 1:06:27.791
-[rumbles]
-[all screaming]

1:06:28.041 --> 1:06:29.375
Ah! No!

1:06:30.916 --> 1:06:33.083
-[squeaks]
-[all screaming]

1:06:33.166 --> 1:06:35.083
[thudding]

1:06:35.166 --> 1:06:37.041
[shrieking]

1:06:38.583 --> 1:06:41.208
[all screaming]

1:06:42.458 --> 1:06:43.750
[groans]

1:06:43.833 --> 1:06:45.250
[all gasp]

1:06:45.333 --> 1:06:47.458
[calm music]

1:06:47.541 --> 1:06:48.833
-Hmm?
-Uh...

1:06:48.916 --> 1:06:50.041
Awesome.

1:06:50.708 --> 1:06:54.250
[all screaming]

1:06:54.708 --> 1:06:56.333
-[whale hums]
-Uh, a whale?

1:06:56.416 --> 1:06:57.583
Uh...

1:06:57.666 --> 1:06:59.625
[gasps, grunting]

1:06:59.708 --> 1:07:01.541
[yelps]

1:07:03.500 --> 1:07:05.375
-[crackles]
-Watch out!

1:07:06.625 --> 1:07:07.958
-[zapping]
-[screams]

1:07:10.000 --> 1:07:13.041
[groaning]

1:07:14.458 --> 1:07:15.500
[Chuck] Is that the...

1:07:15.583 --> 1:07:17.375
eye of the storm?

1:07:17.458 --> 1:07:18.541
Are you kidding?

1:07:18.625 --> 1:07:19.958
The storm's eye is an actual eye?

1:07:20.041 --> 1:07:22.250
-[Booby mutters]
-Well, let's give it a poke.

1:07:22.333 --> 1:07:24.791
This is pretty messed up right here.

1:07:26.083 --> 1:07:27.166
[screams]

1:07:27.250 --> 1:07:28.625
[wood clatters]

1:07:28.708 --> 1:07:31.333
We've got to put that big eye out!

1:07:31.416 --> 1:07:32.458
Come on, you guys!

1:07:32.541 --> 1:07:35.583
[grunting]

1:07:36.666 --> 1:07:38.166
Ready? Fly!

1:07:38.250 --> 1:07:39.208
[whooshing]

1:07:40.750 --> 1:07:42.041
[squawks]

1:07:42.125 --> 1:07:43.208
[whooshes]

1:07:45.125 --> 1:07:46.416
[caws]

1:07:47.083 --> 1:07:48.291
[barks]

1:07:48.375 --> 1:07:51.916
[all grunting]

1:07:52.625 --> 1:07:54.333
[blubbers]

1:07:55.250 --> 1:07:56.083
[yells]

1:07:57.791 --> 1:07:59.708
[gasps]

1:08:01.625 --> 1:08:03.000
[grunting]

1:08:03.083 --> 1:08:05.041
[farting]

1:08:06.166 --> 1:08:07.208
[gasps]

1:08:07.291 --> 1:08:08.333
[thwacks]

1:08:09.375 --> 1:08:10.208
[thuds]

1:08:10.291 --> 1:08:13.208
[thwacking]

1:08:14.791 --> 1:08:15.958
[Yellow shouting]

1:08:16.041 --> 1:08:17.875
-[grunts]
-[roaring]

1:08:21.750 --> 1:08:23.541
Storms have real eyes?

1:08:23.958 --> 1:08:26.541
-It's just so... freaky.
-[manager] Mm-hm.

1:08:27.208 --> 1:08:28.958
[Chuck] If I hadn't seen it
with my own eyes,

1:08:29.083 --> 1:08:30.500
I wouldn't believe it myself.

1:08:30.583 --> 1:08:31.666
[Grace sighs]

1:08:31.750 --> 1:08:33.375
But I promise it's true.

1:08:34.541 --> 1:08:36.041
-But that's bizarre.
-True that.

1:08:36.125 --> 1:08:37.291
Awesome sauce!

1:08:37.375 --> 1:08:39.500
[Granny] Any of them
wear glasses, you think?

1:08:39.583 --> 1:08:41.250
[manager] Darnedest thing I ever heard.

1:08:41.750 --> 1:08:45.541
Um, so, then, tell us
how you got off the island.

1:08:45.625 --> 1:08:46.791
-Yeah!
-[gasps]

1:08:46.875 --> 1:08:48.416
-Yeah.
-Tell us how you escaped!

1:08:48.500 --> 1:08:49.541
Yes, do that!

1:08:49.625 --> 1:08:51.166
-[Grace grunts]
-Did a boat come along?

1:08:51.250 --> 1:08:53.125
-Did you swim across the ocean?
-Huh?

1:08:53.666 --> 1:08:54.833
Get home.

1:08:55.750 --> 1:08:59.000
That's what I was thinking
the whole time I was there.

1:08:59.750 --> 1:09:02.041
[Chuck] But I failed to escape
so many times.

1:09:02.125 --> 1:09:04.791
-I don't even know how many rafts I made.
-Hmm.

1:09:05.208 --> 1:09:06.333
-[Chuck] But, one day...
-Uh?

1:09:06.416 --> 1:09:09.583
...something happened
that meant we had to leave the island.

1:09:09.666 --> 1:09:10.958
[Wendy gasping]

1:09:11.500 --> 1:09:13.583
[Chuck] <i> Ba dup, ba dup, ba ba rap </i>

1:09:13.666 --> 1:09:15.125
<i> Ba-ba ba ba </i>

1:09:15.208 --> 1:09:16.291
<i> Ba rap ba... </i>
[grunts]

1:09:16.375 --> 1:09:17.708
<i> Ba ba da ba... </i>

1:09:17.791 --> 1:09:19.708
-[grunts, sighs]
-[bubbles]

1:09:19.791 --> 1:09:20.833
[water sloshes]

1:09:20.916 --> 1:09:22.625
-[stomach rumbling]
-[water burbles]

1:09:22.708 --> 1:09:24.291
Ah, this is so nice.

1:09:24.375 --> 1:09:25.833
-[rumbling]
-Huh?

1:09:25.916 --> 1:09:28.750
[screaming]

1:09:28.833 --> 1:09:30.500
[spits]
What the...

1:09:30.916 --> 1:09:32.333
[Chuck] A volcano?

1:09:32.416 --> 1:09:33.875
-[explosion]
-[Chuck screams]

1:09:33.958 --> 1:09:35.958
[squawks]

1:09:36.500 --> 1:09:38.458
[harmonizing]

1:09:38.541 --> 1:09:41.166
-[yelps]
-[fireballs thudding]

1:09:41.250 --> 1:09:43.791
[rumbling]

1:09:43.875 --> 1:09:44.833
[grunts]

1:09:44.916 --> 1:09:46.750
Everyone, get on the raft!

1:09:46.833 --> 1:09:48.458
[groans, gasps]

1:09:48.541 --> 1:09:49.750
[screams]

1:09:50.291 --> 1:09:51.916
-[explosion]
-[gasps]

1:09:52.000 --> 1:09:53.375
We need to leave now.

1:09:53.458 --> 1:09:55.083
-[Chuck] Everybody here?
-[robotic mutter]

1:09:56.083 --> 1:09:58.041
[Chuck] Uh, what about the others?

1:09:58.125 --> 1:10:00.166
[mumbles]

1:10:00.250 --> 1:10:02.291
[gasps]
What are they doing?

1:10:02.375 --> 1:10:04.208
[grunting]

1:10:04.625 --> 1:10:06.750
[muttering]

1:10:09.500 --> 1:10:10.833
-[thuds]
-[screams]

1:10:10.916 --> 1:10:12.708
[panting]

1:10:12.791 --> 1:10:13.916
[gasps]

1:10:14.708 --> 1:10:16.458
[Booby grunting]

1:10:16.541 --> 1:10:18.583
[muttering]

1:10:18.666 --> 1:10:20.166
-[coughs]
-[mumbles]

1:10:22.708 --> 1:10:24.375
[rumbling]

1:10:24.708 --> 1:10:27.083
[thumping]

1:10:27.875 --> 1:10:29.416
-[shrieks]
-[Red grunts]

1:10:29.500 --> 1:10:31.125
[groaning]

1:10:31.208 --> 1:10:32.416
[both gasp]

1:10:32.958 --> 1:10:34.333
[whooshes]

1:10:34.416 --> 1:10:35.666
[both scream]

1:10:35.750 --> 1:10:37.500
[loud thud]

1:10:38.333 --> 1:10:39.583
